transmembrane proteins, especially integrins, in a membrane\nenvironment and opens a new way for testing drug binding to integrins under\nclinically relevant conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Dec 2020 21:39:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-22"}
